snippet.title: [Hindi] BMSD 2025 | Survival Stage | Day 2
snippet.description:
The final chance to reach the Grand Finals is here. The 16 remaining teams from the Semi Finals who fell short of the Top 8 now face off in an intense BGMI survival battle. Every match counts and every fight could end their journey. Only the Top 8 teams will move forward to the Grand Finals.

Expect clutch plays, unpredictable zone shifts, and all-out chaos as these teams fight to stay alive and push the game Beyond Limits!

Teams Playing:
Madkings
Blitz Esports
Phoenix Esports
Vasista Esports
iQOO8BIT
OnePlus Cincinnati Kids
Autobotz Esports
mysterious4 Esports
GENESIS ESPORTS 
FS ESPORTS
Likitha Esports
Victores Sumus
Nebula Esports
META NINZA
myG Los Hermanos
First Curiosity

Map Rotation:
Match 1: Erangel
Match 2: Miramar
Match 3: Sanhok
Match 4: Sanhok
Match 5: Miramar
Match 6: Erangel

snippet.title: Tu Subah Hai - Diwali Full Animation | Free Fire MAX
snippet.description:
When love is true, sacrifice follows. When courage rises, legends are born. This Diwali, let emotions ignite the battlefield.

Experience the emotion. Feel the battle. 

Lyrics: 

Tu subah hai,
ya saba hai,
ya koi ishq ka falsafa hai.
Tu dua hai,
ya sazaa hai,
ya koi taaron ki kehkashan hai.
â€‹

Saari dildaari teri,
yeh ishqdaari teri,
sudh-budh khoyi maine,
chadhi hai khumaari teri.
Khud se hua alag,
tujhse mila jo mere,
yaara.... yaara...
tujhse mila toh khud ko haara.
â€‹

Ishq mein tere duniya se kya,
shaitanon se bhi lad jaaun,
bas tujhko hi main paaun.
â€‹
Ek prem hi hai sach,
baaki sab toh yahaan pe jhootha hai re,
mujhko tujh mein mil jaana re, mil jaana re.â€‹

Jab tak meri saans chalti,
mera har ik taana-baana tera hai... tera hai...
Roshni hai jab tak teri mere dil mein,
toh zara bhi na andhera hai... andhera hai...

â€‹Saans meri ruk jaaye toh bhi,
teri khushboo saath mein hogi.
Lau jali meri aankhon mein,
toh jeet apni preet ki hogi.

â€‹
Tu subah hai,
ya saba hai,
ya koi ishq ka falsafa hai.

Featuring the charismatic Sivakarthikeyan and the graceful Rukmini Vasanth in lead roles, this soulful track is composed by none other than Anirudh Ravichander, known for his chart-topping melodies and heart-touching compositions. Thangapoovey blends emotion with melody, capturing the essence of love and longing with poetic visuals and heartfelt lyrics.

With its mesmerizing tune and lyrical depth, Thangapoovey promises to strike a chord with music lovers and fans of Tamil cinema alike. Whether you're a follower of romantic Tamil songs or a die-hard fan of Anirudhâ€™s music, this lyrical video is a must-watch. As anticipation builds for Madharaasi, this song sets the perfect tone, offering a glimpse into the filmâ€™s emotional landscape.
